    "faq": {
      "type": "bnpl-faq",
      "blocks": {
        "q1": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Do you offer Afterpay?", "answer": "<p>Yes. Afterpay is available at checkout on all Proferlo furniture. Choose Afterpay as your payment method and split your order into 4 interest-free payments over 6 weeks. The first payment is taken at checkout and the rest are charged fortnightly.</p>" } },
        "q2": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Can I use Zip Pay on furniture?", "answer": "<p>Yes. Zip Pay can be used on all of our furniture. Select Zip at checkout to buy now and pay over time with flexible weekly, fortnightly or monthly repayments. Zip Pay is always interest-free, though a small monthly account fee may apply if you carry a balance.</p>" } },
        "q3": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "How do I pay with PayPal Pay Later?", "answer": "<p>At checkout, choose PayPal, then select Pay in 4 if it is offered for your order. PayPal splits your purchase into 4 interest-free payments — the first at checkout and the rest every two weeks. There is no interest and no late fees, and PayPal Buyer Protection applies to eligible orders.</p>" } },
        "q4": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Is Buy Now, Pay Later available on all your furniture?", "answer": "<p>Yes. Every item in our store is eligible for Buy Now, Pay Later using Afterpay, Zip or PayPal Pay in 4. There are no excluded products or collections.</p>" } },
        "q5": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Do I pay interest or extra fees with Buy Now, Pay Later?", "answer": "<p>All three providers are interest-free when you pay on time. Afterpay and PayPal Pay in 4 charge no interest; Afterpay may charge a late fee if a payment is missed, while PayPal Pay in 4 has no late fees. Zip Pay is always interest-free but may charge a small monthly account fee if you carry a balance, which is waived when you pay in full. Always check the provider's current terms for full details.</p>" } },
        "q6": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "What is my spending limit?", "answer": "<p>Spending limits are set by each provider based on your individual account and approval — not by Proferlo. When you select a provider at checkout you'll see what you're approved to spend. All of our furniture is eligible, so the only limit is the one your provider sets for you.</p>" } },
        "q7": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Is it safe to use Buy Now, Pay Later at your checkout?", "answer": "<p>Yes. Our checkout is powered by Shopify and is fully encrypted and PCI-DSS compliant. Afterpay, Zip and PayPal are established, regulated Australian payment providers. We never see or store your full card or banking details.</p>" } },
        "q8": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Do I need an account to use Buy Now, Pay Later?", "answer": "<p>Yes — you'll need an account with your chosen provider (Afterpay, Zip or PayPal). Sign-up is quick and you can apply during checkout, with most decisions returned instantly.</p>" } },
        "q9": { "type": "faq", "settings": { "question": "Which Buy Now, Pay Later option should I choose?", "answer": "<p>It comes down to preference. Afterpay and PayPal Pay in 4 both split your order into 4 interest-free fortnightly payments over 6 weeks. Zip Pay offers more flexible weekly, fortnightly or monthly repayments. PayPal Pay in 4 also includes PayPal Buyer Protection. All three are available at our checkout and cover all our furniture.</p>" } },
